Achievements.Name: Son of the cannibal
Achievements.Description: Win the Yellow, Green and Polka-dot jerseys on the same edition with the same rider.

Achievements.Name: Tour legend
Achievements.Description: Win all stages (Tour or One-Off) with the same or different riders.

Achievements.Name: Experienced player
Achievements.Description: Win the Tour de France with a Difficult or Expert team.

Achievements.Name: Dream team
Achievements.Description: Win the Tour de France and have a team-mate on the podium.

Achievements.Name: From start to finish
Achievements.Description: Win the first stage and keep the yellow jersey with same rider throughout all stages of the TDF.

Achievements.Name: Monsieur Tour de France
Achievements.Description: Win at least 5 stages on the same Tour with the same rider (Tour mode only).

Achievements.Name: From nowhere
Achievements.Description: Win a stage with a rider who has no medals (Tour or One-Off).

Achievements.Name: Three in a row
Achievements.Description: Win 3 consecutive stages with the same rider (Tour mode).

Achievements.Name: I live in the mountains
Achievements.Description: Be the first across all Hors Category climbs during the same Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: The baby winner
Achievements.Description: Win the white jersey (tour mode only).

Achievements.Name: King Midas
Achievements.Description: Accumulate more than 500,000 EUR during a Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: King of the sprints
Achievements.Description: Win the green jersey.

Achievements.Name: King of the mountains
Achievements.Description: Win the polka-dot jersey.

Achievements.Name: Welcome to the club
Achievements.Description: Win a Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: First and last
Achievements.Description: Win the first and last stages of the Tour de France in Tour mode.

Achievements.Name: Podium in paris
Achievements.Description: Finish the Tour de France in the top 3 (Tour only).

Achievements.Name: All-rounder
Achievements.Description: Win a stage of each type (Tour or One-off) with any rider of the same team.

Achievements.Name: Support the pressure
Achievements.Description: Wear the yellow jersey for 7 stages with an Expert level team during the same Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: Back-to-back
Achievements.Description: Win 2 consecutive stages with the same rider.

Achievements.Name: Champs Elysees
Achievements.Description: Complete a Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: Like father like son
Achievements.Description: Win a stage with a 30+ rider and with a -25 rider during the same Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: Master of the alliances
Achievements.Description: Create 1 alliances in mode Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: Demolition man
Achievements.Description: Win a stage with more than 2 minutes advance on the 2nd rider.

Achievements.Name: Fast & furious
Achievements.Description: Win a flat stage with a gold medal sprinter.

Achievements.Name: The king of small hills
Achievements.Description: Wear the KOM jersey from the end of the 2nd stage until the 1st mountain stage (Stage 11: Mcon).

Achievements.Name: Faster than you think
Achievements.Description: Wear the green jersey for at least 1 stage with a silver or bronze sprinter.

Achievements.Name: Solo taste better
Achievements.Description: Win a stage with a solo breakaway (at least the last km).

Achievements.Name: Enjoy the victory
Achievements.Description: Use a celebration combo when you win a stage.

Achievements.Name: Raise your arms
Achievements.Description: Your first victory.

Achievements.Name: The harder is still to come
Achievements.Description: Reach the second rest day (stage 17: Pau).

Achievements.Name: Finally some rest
Achievements.Description: Reach the first rest day (stage 10: Mcon).

Achievements.Name: Moto GP
Achievements.Description: Ride faster than 90 km/h.

Achievements.Name: 125cc
Achievements.Description: Ride faster than 70 km/h in a flat section.

Achievements.Name: Rider combativeness prize
Achievements.Description: Be on the first breakaway (E1) for at least 500km during the same Tour de France.

Achievements.Name: I slipped boss!
Achievements.Description: Fall off the bike while wearing the yellow jersey.

Achievements.Name: Attack!!!!!
Achievements.Description: Launch an attack from the peloton to gain a few metres lead.

Achievements.Name: Be my guest
Achievements.Description: Win a quick match in multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Never alone
Achievements.Description: Use all Team Comm menu options, including those only available on mode Full race.

Achievements.Name: TV time for my sponsor
Achievements.Description: Maintain a solo breakaway for, at least, 20 kms.

Achievements.Name: Training complete
Achievements.Description: Complete the full tutorial.
